Create event

Method : POST
URL :
/event/creatEvent

Body (JSON) :
{
"name": "Event 1",
"category": "General",
"capacity": 10,
"available": true,
"date": "2026-02-01"
}

Get all events

Method : GET
URL :
/event/showEvent

Get event by id (only if available = true)

Method : GET
URL :
/event/showEvent/ID_EVENT

Example :
/event/showEvent/695f729271a8d06a453784ad

Update event

Method : PUT
URL :
/event/UpdateEvent/ID_EVENT

Body (JSON) :
{
"capacity": 20,
"date": "2026-03-01"
}

Delete event

Method : DELETE
URL :
/event/DeleteEvent/ID_EVENT

Reservation event (decrease capacity by 1)

Method : GET
URL :
/event/reservationEvent/ID_EVENT


Search event by name and category

Method : GET
URL :
/event/search?name=VivaTech&Category=Technology


Calculate average capacity of available events

Method : GET
URL :
/event/calculate-capacity

Increase capacity by 10% if available = true

Method : PATCH
URL :
/event/ID_EVENT/increase-capacity?available=true

Example :
/event/695f729271a8d06a453784ad/increase-capacity?available=true

Interceptor test (available = false)

Set event available = false

Method : GET
/event/showEvent
or
/event/showEvent/ID_EVENT